<span id="freeTextContainer6251519099362448045">A Masterpiece to learn and understand Renaissance Man. Although, I&apos;m not a painter -- I got a glimpse of Leonardo&apos;s life through his journal entries. <br/><br/>&quot;A Painter is not admirable if he is not universal.&quot; This seems to strike chords with thinkers of School of Salamanca, who viewed Knowledge holistically and didn&apos;t take positivist approach of segmenting branches of Knowledge. <br/><br/><br/>--Deus Vult<br/>Gottfried </span>
